<colgroup>
<col style="width: 33%" />
<col style="width: 33%" />
<col style="width: 33%" />
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr class="odd">
<td data-valign="top"><p>'Chualas nuall an cuan Canach,<br />
Bo a Tiriodh, bo a Barraidh,<br />
Bo a Ile, ’s bo a Arainn,<br />
’S a Cinntire uain a bharraich.</p>
<p>Caillear, caillear, caillear Cuachag,<br />
Caillear Gumag, caillear Guamag,<br />
Caillear Guileag, caillear Guaillionn,<br />
