<p>Lost, lost, lost will be 'Gorag,'<br />
Lost will be 'Dubhag,' lost will be 'Dothag,'<br />
Lost will be 'Muileag,' lost will be 'Moileag,'<br />
And brown 'Muirneag' of the golden hair.</p></td>
</tr>
