Sireadh-thall, sireadh-thall!'</p></td>
<td data-valign="top"><p> </p></td>
<td data-valign="top"><p>Slender-fay, slender-fay!<br />
Mountain-traveller, mountain-traveller!<br />
Black-fairy, black-fairy!<br />
Lucky-treasure, lucky-treasure!<br />
Grey-hound, grey-hound!<br />
Seek-beyond, seek-beyond!</p></td>
